{"tid":592038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鐵馬瞓低扶唔起 交警周星星上身？","createTime":"2018-03-14T02:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T05:54:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f1bd55ed03494c2e2c9b0c811e50642903f43846","tid":592038,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:30:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180314/20331174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F20331174&d=xxv2JTlsdH3wx2T%2F0G90%2FLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=fad59929\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F20331174&h=f9b8a791\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180314/20331174</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有片：鐵馬瞓低扶唔起<br />\n交警周星星上身？ - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n對男士嚟講，「扯唔起」確實好棹忌，何況係男子漢警察？網上熱傳一條交通警多番扶起翻側鐵馬不果嘅短片，片中可見呢名交通警嘅鐵騎向右翻側倒卧馬路中央，警員喺車身右邊，雙手托住車身嘗試推起，但多番嘗試都唔成功，片中有女聲更問：「嘩，好重㗎架車？」後來有熱心市民上前相助，喺鐵馬另一邊拉起，可惜鐵馬都絲毫不動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180314/large/a1303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180314%2Flarge%2Fa1303a.gif&h=51eb4afa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n交通警雙手托鐵馬車身，多番嘗試推起但唔成功。<br />\n<br />\n網民貼片教正確方法<br />\n<br />\n唔少網民留言剝花生，話「警察哥哥想幫手要開聲嘛，如果唔係一陣間又告我毀壞公物」，又質疑警員體能差，有人仲講笑話係周星星（《逃學威龍》周星馳角色）拍緊戲。但都有網民好體諒，話架電單車重量達二三百公斤，加上自身裝備唔少，無力扶正鐵馬都情有可原。<br />\n<br />\n亦有網民好有心，貼上其他影片教點樣正確扶起電單車，話警員應背向車身，一手抓住手柄，一手抓住車身如座位扶手，踎低再以背脊及下肢力量輔助推起，原來警方過往都有拍攝過短片，片中交警側身踎低，雙手抓住扶柄，以下盤力量一把就推起翻側嘅鐵馬，對普羅市民嚟講，今次都算長知識。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180314/large/a1303b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180314%2Flarge%2Fa1303b.gif&h=df644d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱心市民上前相助，<br />\n試圖幫手拉起鐵馬。<br />\n<br />\n識睇睇留言<br />\n<br />\nDannykktsang Tsang：警察都係人，唔識唔緊要，最緊要肯學達者為先<br />\n畢思索：係咪周星星拍緊戲呀！??<br />\nJohn Lam：喺側邊只係笑唔幫手嗰班，全部拉晒告辱警罪。<br />\nWing Chow：可能跌嗰吓拉親肌肉，會短暫腳軟<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：《蘋果》網頁"},{"pid":"861dd7aa14ce8694ad595a1f361830ec6c2c3870","tid":592038,"uid":4210,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:05:03.000Z","msg":"香港警察真係好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜都唔識 淨係識抄牌、知法犯法、做柒事<br />\n紙皮擋水單嘢就睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74910569dec55f0aa1f82f59eed0d36646bcdc37","tid":592038,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:20:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b5e92ac1f00637555c9ae81b717f637f3f9af73","tid":592038,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:23:02.000Z","msg":"wow到"},{"pid":"a6b855a769c021595f5fe36f252812de9b23ff45","tid":592038,"uid":141871,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:29:00.000Z","msg":"樓上果啲未揸過電單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係綿羊仔喎"},{"pid":"cbf2e9f7c74fe613c354210c3e19967abea6f75a","tid":592038,"uid":25900,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a6b855a769c021595f5fe36f252812de9b23ff45","tid":592038,"uid":141871,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:29:00.000Z","msg":"樓上果啲未揸過電單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係綿羊仔喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"你都托唔起呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6b9f83afc3ce19b316a6f91d3980c2977b5275","tid":592038,"uid":160007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:3